{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2070 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2070 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2070","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'type': illegal sizeof operand","pos":[618,648]},{"pos":[655,743],"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>sizeof<ept id=\"p1\">](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md)</ept> operator requires an expression or type name.","source":"The [sizeof](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md) operator requires an expression or type name."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2070:","pos":[750,787]},{"content":"Possible resolution:","pos":[906,926]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2070 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2070\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2070\"\nms.assetid: 4c8dea63-1227-4aba-be26-2462537f86fb\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2070\n'type': illegal sizeof operand  \n  \n The [sizeof](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md) operator requires an expression or type name.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2070:  \n  \n```  \n// C2070.cpp  \nvoid func() {}  \nint main() {  \n   int a;  \n   a = sizeof(func);   // C2070  \n}  \n```  \n  \n Possible resolution:  \n  \n```  \n// C2070b.cpp  \nvoid func() {}  \nint main() {  \n   int a;  \n   a = sizeof(a);  \n}  \n```"}